##########################
# Replica constant       #
##########################

Given php (Php class file with constant):
  <?php

  declare(strict_types=1);

  namespace App;

  final class Test
  {
      private const TEST = 1;
  }

Do (Go to constant and use <C-p>r):
  8j
  \<C-p>rFOO

Expect (Replica of constant):
  <?php

  declare(strict_types=1);

  namespace App;

  final class Test
  {
      private const TEST = 1;

      private const FOO = 1;
  }

